@prefix isoiec80000: <https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/> .
@prefix smart: <https://w3id.org/standards/smart/ontologies/core/> .
@prefix dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> .
@prefix skosxl: <http://www.w3.org/2008/05/skos-xl#> .

isoiec80000:part-11-4 a smart:PublicationDocument ;
  dcterms:title "Part 11-4"@en ;
  dcterms:identifier "ISO 80000-11-4" ;
  smart:hasPublicationType smart:internationalStandard ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.1-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Reynolds number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.1-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Re"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.1 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.1" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.1-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.1-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of inertial forces and viscous forces in a fluid flow, expressed by

stem:[Re = (rho v l)/eta = (v l)/sf(ii(v))]; where

stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>),
stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[eta]:: is dynamic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>), and
stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The value of the Reynolds number gives an estimate on the flow state: laminar flow or turbulent flow.

In rotating movement, the speed stem:[v= omega l], where stem:[l] is the distance from the rotation axis and stem:[omega] is the angular velocity.
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.2-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Euler number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.2-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Eu"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.2 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.2" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.2-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.2-0 ;
  skos:definition """relationship between pressure drop in a flow and the kinetic energy per volume for flow of fluids in a pipe, expressed by

stem:[Eu = (Delta p)/(rho v^2)]; where

stem:[Delta p]:: is drop of pressure (<<iso80000-4>>),
stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>), and
stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Euler number is used to characterize losses in the flow.

A modification of the Euler number is considering the dimensions of the containment (pipe):

stem:[Eu' = d/l Eu]; where

stem:[d]:: is inner diameter (<<iso80000-3>>) of the pipe, and
stem:[l]:: is length (<<iso80000-3>>).
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.3-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Froude number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.3-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Fr"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.3 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.3" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.3-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.3-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of a body's inertial forces and its gravitational forces for flow of fluids, expressed by

stem:[Fr = v/(sqrt(lg))]; where

stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>) of flow,
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>), and
stem:[g]:: is acceleration of free fall (<<iso80000-3>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Froude number can be modified by buoyancy.

Sometimes the square and sometimes the inverse of the Froude number as defined here is wrongly used.
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.4-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Grashof number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.4-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Gr"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.4 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.4" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.4-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.4-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of buoyancy forces due to thermal expansion which results in a change of mass density and viscous forces for free convection due to temperature differences, expressed by

stem:[Gr = l^3 g alpha_V Delta T // sf(ii(v))^2]; where

stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[g]:: is acceleration of free fall (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[alpha_V]:: is thermal cubic expansion coefficient (<<iso80000-5>>),
stem:[Delta T]:: is difference of thermodynamic temperature stem:[T] (<<iso80000-5>>) between surface of the body and the fluid far away from the body, and
stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """Heating can occur near hot vertical walls, in pipes, or by a bluff body.

The characteristic length can be the vertical height of a hot plate, the diameter of a pipe, or the effective length of a body.

See also Rayleigh number (<<t11-5.3>>).
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.5-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Weber number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.5-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "We"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.5 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.5" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.5-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.5-0 ;
  skos:definition """relation between inertial forces and capillary forces due to surface tension at the interface between two different fluids, expressed by

stem:[We = rho v^2 l // gamma]; where

stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>),
stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>), and
stem:[gamma]:: is surface tension (<<iso80000-4>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The fluids can be gases or liquids.

The different fluids often are drops moving in a gas or bubbles in a liquid.

The characteristic length is commonly the diameter of bubbles or drops.

The square root of the Weber number is called Rayleigh number.

Sometimes the square root of the Weber number as defined here is called the Weber number. That definition is deprecated.

Interfaces only exist between two fluids which are not miscible.
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.6-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Mach number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.6-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Ma"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.6 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.6" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.6-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.6-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of the speed of flow and the speed of sound, expressed by

stem:[Ma = v//c]; where

stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>) of the body, and
stem:[c]:: is speed of sound (<<iso80000-8>>) in the fluid
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Mach number represents the relationship of inertial forces compared to compression forces.

For an ideal gas

stem:[c = sqrt(gamma p/rho) = sqrt(gamma (RT)/M) = sqrt(gamma (kT)/m)]; where stem:[gamma] is ratio of the specific heat capacity (<<iso80000-5>>).
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.7-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Knudsen number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.7-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Kn"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.7 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.7" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.7-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.7-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of free path length of a particle and a characteristic length, expressed by

stem:[Kn = lambda // l]; where

stem:[lambda]:: is mean free path (<<iso80000-9>>), and
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Knudsen number is a measure to estimate whether the gas in flow behaves like a continuum.

The characteristic length, stem:[l], can be a characteristic size of the gas flow region like a pipe diameter.
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.8-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Strouhal number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.8-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Thomson number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.8-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Sr"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.8-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Sh"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.8 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.8" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.8-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.8-1 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.8-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.8-1 ;
  skos:definition """relation between a characteristic frequency and a characteristic speed for unsteady flow with periodic behaviour, expressed by

stem:[Sr = fl // v]; where

stem:[f]:: is frequency (<<iso80000-3>>) of vortex shedding,
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>), and
stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>) of flow
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The characteristic length, stem:[l], can be the diameter of an obstacle in the flow which can cause vortex shedding, or the length of it."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.9-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "drag coefficient"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.9-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "c_\"D\""@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.9 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.9" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.9-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.9-0 ;
  skos:definition """relation between the effective drag force and inertial forces for a body moving in a fluid, expressed by

stem:[c_\"D\" = (2F_\"D\")/(rho v^2 A)]; where

stem:[F_\"D\"]:: is drag force (<<iso80000-4>>) on the body,
stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid,
stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>) of the body, and
stem:[A]:: is cross-sectional area (<<iso80000-3>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The drag coefficient is strongly dependant on the shape of the body."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.10-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Bagnold number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.10-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Bg"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.10 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.10" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.10-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.10-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of drag force and gravitational force for a body moving in a fluid, expressed by

stem:[Bg = (c_\"D\"rho v^2)/(l g rho_\"b\")]; where

stem:[c_\"D\"]:: is drag coefficient (<<t11-4.9>>) of the body,
stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid,
stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>) of the body,
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[g]:: is acceleration of free fall (<<iso80000-3>>), and
stem:[rho_\"b\"]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of the body
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The characteristic length, stem:[l], is the body's volume divided by its cross-sectional area."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.11-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Bagnold number <solid particles>"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.11-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Ba_2"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.11 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.11" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.11-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.11-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of drag force and viscous force in a fluid transferring solid particles, expressed by

stem:[Ba_2 = (rho_\"s\" d^2 dot gamma)/eta sqrt(1//(f_\"s\"^(1//2)-1))]; where

stem:[rho_\"s\"]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of particles,
stem:[d]:: is diameter (<<iso80000-3>>) of particles,
stem:[dot gamma = v//d]:: is shear rate time-derivative of shear strain (<<iso80000-4>>),
stem:[eta]:: is dynamic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>) of fluid, and
stem:[f_\"s\"]:: is volumic fraction of solid particles
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.12-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "lift coefficient"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.12-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "c_\"l\""@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.12-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "c_\"A\""@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.12 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.12" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.12-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.12-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.12-1 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of the lift force available from a wing at a given angle and the inertial force for a wing shaped body moving in a fluid, expressed by

stem:[c_\"l\" = (2F_\"l\")/(rho v^2 S) = F_\"l\"/(qS)]; where

stem:[F_\"l\"]:: is lift force (<<iso80000-4>>) on the wing,
stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid,
stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>) of the body,
stem:[S = A\" cos \"alpha]:: is effective area (<<iso80000-3>>) when stem:[alpha] is the angle of attack and stem:[A] is area of the wing, and
stem:[q=rho v^2//2]:: is dynamic pressure.
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The lift coefficient is dependant on the shape of the wing."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.13-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "thrust coefficient"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.13-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "c_\"t\""@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.13 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.13" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.13-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.13-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of the effective thrust force available from a propeller and the inertial force in a fluid, expressed by

stem:[c_\"t\" = F_\"T\" // (rho n^2 d^4)]; where

stem:[F_\"T\"]:: is thrust force (<<iso80000-4>>) of the propeller,
stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid,
stem:[n]:: is rotational frequency (<<iso80000-3>>), and
stem:[d]:: is tip diameter (<<iso80000-3>>) of the propeller
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The thrust coefficient is dependant on the shape of the propeller."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.14-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Dean number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.14-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Dn"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.14 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.14" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.14-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.14-0 ;
  skos:definition """relation between centrifugal force and inertial force, for flows of fluids in curved pipes, expressed by

stem:[Dn = (2vr)/sf(ii(v)) sqrt(r/R)]; where

stem:[v]:: is (axial) speed (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[r]:: is radius (<<iso80000-3>>) of the pipe,
stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid, and
stem:[R]:: is radius of curvature (<<iso80000-3>>) of the path of the pipe
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.15-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Bejan number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.15-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Be"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.15 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.15" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.15-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.15-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of mechanical work and frictional energy loss in fluid dynamics in a pipe, expressed by

stem:[Be = (Delta p l^2)/(eta sf(ii(v))) = (rho Delta p l^2)/eta^2]; where

stem:[Delta p]:: is drop of pressure (<<iso80000-4>>) along the pipe,
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[eta]:: is dynamic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>),
stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>), and
stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>).
"""@en ;
  skos:note """A similar number exists for heat transfer (<<t11-5.9>>).

The kinematic viscosity is also called momentum diffusivity.
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.16-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Lagrange number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.16-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Lg"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.16 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.16" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.16-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.16-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of mechanical work and frictional energy loss in fluid dynamics in a pipe, expressed by

stem:[Lg = (l Delta p)/(eta v)]; where

stem:[l]:: is length (<<iso80000-3>>) of the pipe,
stem:[Delta p]:: is drop of pressure (<<iso80000-4>>) along the pipe,
stem:[eta]:: is dynamic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>), and
stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Lagrange number is also given by

stem:[La = Re * Eu]; where

stem:[Re]:: is the Reynolds number (<<t11-4.1>>), and
stem:[Eu]:: is the Euler number (<<t11-4.2>>).
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.17-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Bingham number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.17-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "plasticity number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.17-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Bm"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.17-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Bn"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.17 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.17" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.17-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.17-1 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.17-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.17-1 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of yield stress and viscous stress in a viscous material for flow of viscoplastic material in channels, expressed by

stem:[Bm = (tau d)/(eta v)]; where

stem:[tau]:: is shear stress (<<iso80000-4>>),
stem:[d]:: is characteristic diameter (<<iso80000-3>>), e.g. effective channel width,
stem:[eta]:: is dynamic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>), and
stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>)
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.18-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Hedström number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.18-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "He"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.18-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Hd"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.18 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.18" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.18-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.18-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.18-1 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of yield stress and viscous stress of a viscous material at flow limit for visco-plastic material in a channel, expressed by

stem:[He = (tau_0 d^2 rho)/eta^2]; where

stem:[tau_0]:: is shear stress (<<iso80000-4>>) at flow limit,
stem:[d]:: is characteristic diameter (<<iso80000-3>>), e.g. effective channel width,
stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>), and
stem:[eta]:: is dynamic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>)
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.19-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Bodenstein number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.19-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Bd"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.19 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.19" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.19-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.19-0 ;
  skos:definition """mathematical expression of the transfer of matter by convection in reactors with respect to diffusion,

stem:[Bd = vl//D]; where

stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[l]:: is length (<<iso80000-3>>) of the reactor, and
stem:[D]:: is diffusion coefficient (<<iso80000-9>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Bodenstein number is also given by

stem:[Bd = Pe** = Re * Sc]; where

stem:[Pe**]:: is the Péclet number for mass transfer (<<t11-6.2>>),
stem:[Re]:: is the Reynolds number (<<t11-4.1>>), and
stem:[Sc = eta//(rho D) = v//D]:: is Schmidt number (<<t11-7.2>>).
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.20-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Rossby number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.20-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Kiebel number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.20-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Ro"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.20 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.20" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.20-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.20-1 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.20-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of inertial forces and Coriolis forces in the context of transfer of matter in geophysics, expressed by

stem:[Ro = v//(2 l omega_\"E\" \"sin\"varphi)]; where

stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>) of motion,
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>), the scale of the phenomenon,
stem:[omega_\"E\"]:: is angular velocity (<<iso80000-3>>) of the Earth's rotation, and
stem:[varphi]:: is angle (<<iso80000-3>>) of latitude
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Rossby number represents the effect of Earth's rotation on flow in pipes, rivers, ocean currents, tornadoes, etc.

The quantity stem:[omega_\"E\" \"sin\"varphi] is called Coriolis frequency.
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.21-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Ekman number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.21-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Ek"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.21 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.21" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.21-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.21-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of viscous forces and Coriolis forces in the context of transfer of matter for the flow of a rotating fluid, expressed by

stem:[Ek = sf(ii(v))//(2l^2 omega_\"E\" \"sin\"varphi)]; where

stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>),
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>), the scale of the phenomenon,
stem:[omega_\"E\"]:: is angular frequency (<<iso80000-3>>) of the Earth's rotation, and
stem:[varphi]:: is angle of latitude
"""@en ;
  skos:note """In plasma physics, the square root of this number is used.

The Ekman number is also given by

stem:[Ek = Ro//Re]; where

stem:[Ro]:: is the Rossby number (<<t11-4.20>>), and
stem:[Re]:: is the Reynolds number (<<t11-4.1>>).
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.22-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "elasticity number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.22-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "El"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.22 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.22" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.22-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.22-0 ;
  skos:definition """relation between relaxation time and diffusion time in viscoelastic flows, expressed by

stem:[El = t_\"r\" sf(ii(v))//r^2]; where

stem:[t_\"r\"]:: is relaxation time (<<iso80000-12>>),
stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>), and
stem:[r]:: is radius (<<iso80000-3>>) of pipe
"""@en ;
  skos:note """See also Deborah number (<<t11-7.8>>)."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.23-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Darcy friction factor"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.23-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Moody friction factor"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.23-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "f_\"D\""@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.23 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.23" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.23-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.23-1 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.23-0 ;
  skos:definition """representation of pressure loss in a pipe due to friction within a laminar or turbulent flow of a fluid in a pipe, expressed by

stem:[f_\"D\" = (2 Delta p)/(rho v^2) d/l]; where

stem:[Delta p]:: is drop of pressure (<<iso80000-4>>) due to friction,
stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid,
stem:[v]:: is (average) speed (<<iso80000-3>>) of the fluid in the pipe,
stem:[d]:: is diameter (<<iso80000-3>>) of the pipe, and
stem:[l]:: is length (<<iso80000-3>>) of the pipe
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.24-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Fanning number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.24-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "f_\"n\""@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.24-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "f"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.24 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.24" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.24-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.24-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.24-1 ;
  skos:definition """relation between shear stress and dynamic pressure in the flow of a fluid in a containment, expressed by

stem:[f_\"n\" = (2 tau)/(rho v^2)]; where

stem:[tau]:: is shear stress (<<iso80000-4>>) at the wall,
stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid, and
stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>) of the fluid in the pipe
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Fanning number describes the flow of fluids in a pipe with friction at the walls represented by its shear stress.

Symbol stem:[f] may be used where no conflicts are possible.
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.25-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Goertler number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.25-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Goertler parameter"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.25-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Go"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.25 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.25" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.25-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.25-1 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.25-0 ;
  skos:definition """characterization of the stability of laminar boundary layer flows in transfer of matter in a boundary layer on curved surfaces, expressed by

stem:[Go = (v l_\"b\")/sf(ii(v)) sqrt((l_\"b\"/r_\"c\"))]; where

stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[l_\"b\"]:: is boundary layer thickness (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>), and
stem:[r_\"c\"]:: is radius of curvature (<<iso80000-3>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Goertler number represents the ratio of centrifugal effects to viscous effects."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.26-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Hagen number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.26-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Hg"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.26-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Ha"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.26 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.26" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.26-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.26-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.26-1 ;
  skos:definition """generalization of the Grashof number for forced or free convection in laminar flow, expressed by

stem:[Hg = -1/rho (\"d\"p)/(\"d\"x) l^3/v^2]; where

stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of fluid,
stem:[(\"d\"p)/(\"d\"x)]:: is gradient of pressure (<<iso80000-4>>),
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>), and
stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """For free thermal convection with stem:[(\"d\"p)/(\"d\"x) = rho g alpha_\"V\" Delta T], the Hagen number then coincides with the Grashof number (<<t11-4.4>>). See also the Poiseuille number (<<t11-4.28>>)."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.27-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Laval number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.27-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "La"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.27 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.27" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.27-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.27-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of speed and the (critical) sound speed at the throat of a nozzle, expressed by

stem:[La = v // sqrt((R_\"s\"T 2 gamma)//(gamma + 1))]; where

stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[R_\"s\" = R/M]:: is specific gas constant, where
stem:[R]::: is molar gas constant (<<iso80000-9>>), and
stem:[M]::: is molar mass (<<iso80000-9>>),
stem:[T]:: is thermodynamic temperature (<<iso80000-5>>), and
stem:[gamma]:: is ratio of the specific heat capacities (<<iso80000-5>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Laval number is a specific kind of Mach number (<<t11-4.6>>)."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.28-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Poiseuille number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.28-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Poi"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.28 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.28" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.28-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.28-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of propulsive force by pressure and viscous force for a flow of fluids in a pipe, expressed by

stem:[Poi = (Delta p)/l d^2/(eta v)]; where

stem:[Delta p]:: is drop of pressure (<<iso80000-4>>) along the pipe,
stem:[l]:: is length (<<iso80000-3>>) of the pipe,
stem:[d]:: is diameter (<<iso80000-3>>) of the pipe,
stem:[eta]:: is dynamic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid, and
stem:[v]:: is characteristic speed (<<iso80000-3>>) of the fluid
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Poiseuille number is stem:[Poi=32] for laminar flow in a round pipe.

See also the Hagen number (<<t11-4.26>>).
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.29-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "power number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.29-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Pn"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.29 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.29" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.29-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.29-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of power consumption by agitators due to drag and rotational inertial power in fluids, expressed by

stem:[Pn = P//(rho n^3d^5)]; where

stem:[P]:: is active power (<<iec80000-6>>) consumed by a stirrer,
stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of fluid,
stem:[n]:: is rotational frequency (<<iso80000-3>>), and
stem:[d]:: is diameter (<<iso80000-3>>) of stirrer
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.30-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Richardson number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.30-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Ri"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.30 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.30" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.30-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.30-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of potential energy and kinetic energy for a falling body, expressed by

stem:[Ri = gh//v^2]; where

stem:[g]:: is acceleration of free fall (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[h]:: is characteristic height (<<iso80000-3>>), and
stem:[v]:: is characteristic speed (<<iso80000-3>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """In geophysics differences of these quantities are of interest."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.31-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Reech number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.31-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Ree"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.31 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.31" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.31-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.31-0 ;
  skos:definition """relation between the speed of an object submerged in water relative to the water, and wave propagation speed, expressed by

stem:[Ree = sqrt(gl)//v]; where

stem:[g]:: is acceleration of free fall (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>), and
stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>) of the object relative to the water
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Reech number can be used to determine the resistance of a partially submerged object (e.g. a ship) of length stem:[l] (in direction of the motion) moving through water.

A similar quantity is defined as the Boussinesq number stem:[Bs = v//sqrt(2gl)].
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.32-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Stokes number <time-related>"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.32-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Stk"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.32 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.32" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.32-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.32-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of friction and inertia forces for particles in a fluid or in a plasma, expressed by

stem:[Stkt = t_\"r\"//t_\"a\"]; where

stem:[t_\"r\"]:: is relaxation time (<<iso80000-12>>) of particles to achieve fluid's velocity due to friction (viscosity), and
stem:[t_\"a\"]:: is time (<<iso80000-3>>) of fluid to alter its velocity under external influence
"""@en ;
  skos:note """In most cases stem:[t_\"r\"=l//v]; where stem:[l] is characteristic length, and stem:[v] is speed of fluid. The characteristic length can be the diameter of an obstacle or hole."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.33-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Stokes number <vibrating particles>"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.33-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Stk_1"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.33 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.33" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.33-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.33-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of friction and inertia forces for the special case of particles vibrating in a fluid or plasma, expressed by

stem:[Stk_1 = sf(ii(v)) // (d^2f)]; where

stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid or plasma,
stem:[d]:: is diameter (<<iso80000-3>>) of particle, and
stem:[f]:: is frequency (<<iso80000-3>>) of particle vibrations
"""@en ;
  skos:note """Sometimes the inverse of this number is wrongly used."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.34-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Stokes number <rotameter>"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.34-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "power coefficient <rotameter>"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.34-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Stk_2"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.34 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.34" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.34-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.34-1 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.34-0 ;
  skos:definition """Stokes number for calibration of rotameters metering vertical flows of fluids by means of a floating body, expressed by

stem:[Stk_2 = {r^3 g m rho}/{eta^2} {(rho_{\"b\"} - rho)}/{rho_{\"b\"}} = {r^3 g m}/{v^2} (1/{rho} - 1/{rho_{\"b\"}})]; where

stem:[r]:: is ratio of pipe and float radii,
stem:[g]:: is acceleration of free fall (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[m]:: is mass (<<iso80000-4>>) of the body,
stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid,
stem:[eta]:: is dynamic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid,
stem:[rho_\"b\"]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of the body, and
stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid
"""@en ;
  skos:note """In general use, this value is multiplied by stem:[1.042].

See also the Archimedes number (<<t11-6.12>>).
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.35-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Stokes number <gravity>"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.35-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Stk_3"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.35 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.35" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.35-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.35-0 ;
  skos:definition """relation between viscous forces and gravity forces for particles falling in a fluid, expressed by

stem:[Stk_3 = v sf(ii(v)) // (gl^2)]; where

stem:[v]:: is characteristic speed (<<iso80000-3>>) of particles,
stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid,
stem:[g]:: is acceleration of free fall (<<iso80000-3>>), and
stem:[l]:: is length (<<iso80000-3>>) of fall
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.36-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Stokes number <drag>"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.36-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Stk_4"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.36 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.36" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.36-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.36-0 ;
  skos:definition """quotient of drag force and internal friction forces for particles dragged in a fluid

stem:[Stk_4=F_\"D\"//(eta v l)]; where

stem:[F_\"D\"]:: is drag force (<<iso80000-4>>),
stem:[eta]:: is dynamic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>),
stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>), and
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>)
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.37-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Laplace number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.37-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Suratman number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.37-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "La"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.37-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Su"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.37 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.37" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.37-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.37-1 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.37-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.37-1 ;
  skos:definition """relation between capillary forces and viscous forces when characterizing free surface flow, expressed by

stem:[La = Su = gamma p l // eta^2]; where

stem:[gamma]:: is surface tension (<<iso80000-4>>),
stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid,
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>), and
stem:[eta]:: is dynamic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Laplace number is also the ratio of surface tension to momentum transfer, especially dissipation, inside a fluid.

The Laplace number is also given by

stem:[La = Su = 1//Oh^2 = Re^2//We]; where

stem:[Oh]:: is the Ohnesorge number (<<t11-7.4>>),
stem:[Re]:: is the Reynolds number (<<t11-4.1>>), and
stem:[We]:: is the Weber number (<<t11-4.5>>).
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.38-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Blake number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.38-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Bl"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.38 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.38" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.38-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.38-0 ;
  skos:definition """relation between inertial forces and viscous forces in a porous material, expressed by

stem:[Bl = (vpl)/(eta(1-epsilon))]; where

stem:[v]:: is speed (<<iso80000-3>>) of the fluid,
stem:[rho]:: is mass density (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid,
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>) defined as the volume of a particle divided by its surface area,
stem:[eta]:: is dynamic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid, and
stem:[epsilon]:: is porosity of the material (=void fraction)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Blake number can be interpreted as a Reynolds number for flow in porous material."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.39-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Sommerfeld number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.39-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "So"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.39-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Sm"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.39 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.39" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.39-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.39-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.39-1 ;
  skos:definition """relation between viscous force and load force in a lubrication boundary, expressed by

stem:[So = (eta n)/p (r/c)^2]; where

stem:[eta]:: is dynamic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>) of the lubricant,
stem:[n]:: is rotational frequency (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[p]:: is mean bearing pressure (<<iso80000-4>>),
stem:[r]:: is radius (<<iso80000-3>>) of the shaft, and
stem:[c]:: is radial distance (<<iso80000-3>>) between rotating shaft and annulus
"""@en ;
  skos:note """Sometimes the inverse of this number is wrongly used."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.40-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Taylor number <momentum transfer>"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.40-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Ta"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.40 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.40" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.40-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.40-0 ;
  skos:definition """relation between centrifugal force and viscous force of a rotating shaft, expressed by

stem:[Ta = 4 omega^2 l^4 // sf(ii(v))^2]; where

stem:[omega]:: is angular velocity (<<iso80000-3>>) of rotation,
stem:[l]:: is length (<<iso80000-3>>) perpendicular to the rotation axis, and
stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """Sometimes the square root of this quantity is wrongly used.

The Taylor number for a rotating shaft relative to an annulus is given by

stem:[Ta_\"a\" = (omega//sf(ii(v)))^2 ra^3]; where

stem:[omega]:: is angular velocity (<<iso80000-3>>) of the shaft,
stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>),
stem:[r = (r_2+r_1)//2]:: is mean radius (<<iso80000-3>>) of the annulus, and
stem:[a = (r_2-r_1)]:: is width of the annulus, where
stem:[r_1]::: is inner radius of the annulus, and
stem:[r_2]::: is outer radius of the annulus.

Sometimes the square root of this quantity is used; this use is deprecated.
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.41-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Galilei number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.41-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Ga"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.41 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.41" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.41-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.41-0 ;
  skos:definition """relation between gravitational force and viscous force in fluid films flowing over walls, expressed by

stem:[Ga = gl^3 // sf(ii(v))^2]; where

stem:[g]:: is acceleration of free fall (<<iso80000-3>>),
stem:[l]:: is characteristic length (<<iso80000-3>>), and
stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>) of the fluid
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Galilei number is also given by

stem:[Ga = Re^2 * Ri] or +
stem:[Ga = Re^2 // Fr^2]; where

stem:[Re]:: is the Reynolds number (<<t11-4.1>>),
stem:[Ri]:: is the Richardson number (<<t11-4.30>>), and
stem:[Fr]:: is the Froude number (<<t11-4.3>>).
"""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .

isoiec80000:term-t11-4.42-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Womersley number"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:fullForm .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.42-0 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "Wo"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.42-1 a smart:Term, skosxl:Label ;
  skosxl:literalForm "alpha"@en ;
  smart:hasTermFormType smart:symbol .

isoiec80000:t11-4.42 a isoiec80000:Quantity, smart:TermEntry ;
  dcterms:identifier "11-4.42" ;
  skosxl:prefLabel isoiec80000:term-t11-4.42-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.42-0 ;
  skosxl:altLabel isoiec80000:sym-t11-4.42-1 ;
  skos:definition """relation between inertial forces and viscous forces in oscillating flows of fluids in pipes, expressed by

stem:[Wo = R sqrt(omega//sf(ii(v)))]; where

stem:[R]:: is (effective) radius (<<iso80000-3>>) of the pipe,
stem:[omega]:: is angular frequency (<<iso80000-3>>) of oscillations, and
stem:[sf(ii(v))]:: is kinematic viscosity (<<iso80000-4>>)
"""@en ;
  skos:note """The Womersley number is used for pulsating flows e.g. in blood flow."""@en ;
  smart:hasBindingnessType smart:normative ;
  dcterms:isPartOf isoiec80000:part-11-4 .
